title: Southridge High School students show support for breast cancer awareness
text: October 1, 2015 Southridge High School students show support for breast cancer awareness The students at Southridge High School, many wearing bright pink clothing, stand in the shape of a breast cancer ribbon Thursday morning outside on the Kennewick school's athletic field.
